channel.title: Help with "Bank Full!" On PhoneScape
channel.description: Yes well, when i sell a PHAT to Santa, i get 2147Mill, It says "Bank Full!" When i try to deposit another 2147Mill, after i have already deposited 2147Mill. I am using PhoneScape, Help would be much appreciated. I have searched for "Bank Full!" In Client.Java, but their is too many to know which one it is. Help is greatly appreciated, Thanks.
